BugReports: https://github.com/Dripdrop12/RInno/issues
Description: This package helps you deploy local shiny apps using Inno Setup, an open source software that builds installers for Windows with a complete feature set to manage software deployments. It can be used to deploy local Shiny applications, reports or R scripts like any other application with an installer.
